text: Khlebodarovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Alexandrovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 253 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Meleuz, 9 km from Alexandrovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Khlebodarovka, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
